"""Test for 5 existing outputfiles"""
print('download path: ', cluster_download_path)
outputfilelist = [item for item in os.listdir(cluster_download_path.
    as_posix()) if 'tonic_depol_level' in item]
assert len([item for item in outputfilelist if os.access(
    cluster_download_path.joinpath(item), os.W_OK)]) == 6
metafiles = [item for item in os.listdir(cluster_download_path.as_posix()) if
    'metadata_' in item]
assert len([item for item in metafiles if os.access(cluster_download_path.
    joinpath(item), os.W_OK)]) == 2
